{"tid":2204294,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"國台辦發言人馬曉光: 台灣問題是中國內政，不允許外部勢力插手干涉","createTime":"2020-09-16T03:11:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-16T04:15:30.000Z","uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2a07cabd7c159bdce42c3574a2ea9d081a059d1e","tid":2204294,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T03:11:42.000Z","msg":"美國和台灣將舉行經濟與商業對話，美國國務次卿克拉奇將到台灣出席。<br />\n<br />\n在北京，國台辦發言人馬曉光回應時重申，台灣問題是中國內政，不允許外部勢力插手干涉，要求美方恪守一個中國原則和中美三個聯合公報規定，停止同中國台灣地區開展任何形式的官方往來。<br />\n<br />\n他說，民進黨當局不顧民意反對，為政治目的執意開放有問題的美國農畜產品進口台灣，損害民眾健康福祉，現在又打著經濟商業幌子，同美國發展官方關係，只會進一步任由美方宰割，衝擊島內市場和損害台灣同胞經濟民生利益。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1549863-20200916.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1549863-20200916.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=%2F2JumwqaKkMO2nYek6mTvSZO8jd1M6XCUNMtuDfdPZA%3D&h=deb1150c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1549863-20200916.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=212e9abd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1549863-20200916.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"c709485fe137592c30bc92d11c6c4e0066b46059","tid":2204294,"uid":98551,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T03:16:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5f273dd04eeddc200ae430a656e25847bed948c","tid":2204294,"uid":59461,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T03:17:34.000Z","msg":"征服波蘭係德國內政<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c10d2648bf72ee4fbdcd0a110f6058c05bd2d677","tid":2204294,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-16T03:51:06.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"f649fdc1ec310c6d748dc2b9fbfc687584a57eee","tid":2204294,"uid":240676,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-